    <item>
      <title>顶级矿业公司必和必拓 (BHP) 削减了镍项目 25% 的劳动力：AFR</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/top-miner-bhp-stands-down-25-of-nickel-project-workforce-afr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《澳大利亚金融评论报》报道，全球最大的矿业公司必和必拓集团已解雇了西澳大利亚西马斯格雷夫镍铜项目建设中约四分之一的工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/top-miner-bhp-stands-down-25-of-nickel-project-workforce-afr</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 06:39:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
